bdremote-ng 0.4
---------------

Adds support for repeating a key (after an initial delay), when its being held down. Also adds doxygen comments.

002 Implement support for repeat.
008 Add doxygen comments for all interfaces.
015 Running in background results in no remote control.
017 Add doxygen for all files.

